      <title>Moon from the Stars - Jeff&amp;#039;s ACWW Blog</title>
      <author>Jeff</author>
      <link>https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2024/12/13/moon-from-the-stars/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2024/12/13/moon-from-the-stars/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 14 Dec 2024 03:23:32 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;article id="post-7831" class="post-7831 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized"&gt; 	&lt;header class="entry-header"&gt; 		&lt;h1 class="entry-title"&gt;Moon from the Stars&lt;/h1&gt;	&lt;/header&gt;&lt;!-- .entry-header --&gt;  	 	 	&lt;div class="entry-content"&gt; 		 &lt;p&gt;Snow now covers the ground in Wild World (and the other Animal Crossing games as well). It&amp;#8217;s a pretty time of year, although I know we&amp;#8217;ll all be sick of the snow in a month or so. 😆&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;On Wednesday, Truffles interrupted me as I was hitting the money rock. She prevented me from getting the full payout!&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img fetchpriority="high" width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/truffles-chat-150x112.jpg" alt="Truffles: So you wanna chat with me some more, right? Yeah, I like chatting with me, too!" class="wp-image-7832" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;figcaption class="wp-element-caption"&gt;You just cost me a few thousand bells!&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Caroline told me that she&amp;#8217;s (finally) over her cold, and she thanked me for the medicine by giving me a concrete wall. This will surely help us &lt;em&gt;cement &lt;/em&gt;our friendship. 😛&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;After I came out of Whitney&amp;#8217;s house, a shooting star flew overhead! Fortunately, I was able to wish on it before it zoomed out of sight.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/star-121124-150x112.jpg" alt="A shooting star flies by overhead." class="wp-image-7833" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;The next day, I received a letter from Wishy in the mail. He sent me the moon! That&amp;#8217;s a pretty big gift! I wonder how much he had to pay for shipping&amp;#8230;the cost must&amp;#8217;ve been astronomical! In fact, I&amp;#8217;m sure it eclipses any shipping cost I&amp;#8217;ve ever observed! 🌚&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Tank was talking about pouring some miso soup over pear salad, and he asked what I thought of that. A slider popped up with the two extreme options being &amp;#8220;So good!&amp;#8221; and &amp;#8220;Awful!&amp;#8221; I moved it just a tiny bit below the midpoint, and Tank became furious at me.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/tank-snobby-150x112.jpg" alt="Tank: Oh, c'mon! Come down off your snobby horse and try something unique!" class="wp-image-7834" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;figcaption class="wp-element-caption"&gt;Sorry, I&amp;#8217;m not feeling &lt;em&gt;soup&lt;/em&gt;-er adventurous today.&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Filbert asked me for a fossil, so I gave him a fern fossil that I dug up. He was happy with it, and he rewarded me with a plaza wall.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Today, Mom sent me a letter about drinking cocoa around the holidays. She also sent me an apple, which is a foreign fruit. But it&amp;#8217;s also a fruit I already had, so it wasn&amp;#8217;t super useful. But still, it is nice to be able to get foreign fruit this way.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Drift jokingly wondered if Curt and Filbert could be brothers. Yeah, I don&amp;#8217;t think so. 😛&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/drift-brothers-150x112.jpg" alt="Drift: Wouldn't it be funny if Curt and Filbert turned out to be brothers?" class="wp-image-7835" sizes="auto, (max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;figcaption class="wp-element-caption"&gt;Come on, they &lt;em&gt;bearly &lt;/em&gt;look related.&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;When I visited Filbert, he was still talking about the fossil I gave him yesterday. He said he was so excited that he couldn&amp;#8217;t help but dance! &lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/filbert-excited-150x112.jpg" alt="Filbert: I'm so excited that I can't help but dance! Shake it! Woot!" class="wp-image-7836" sizes="auto, (max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;See, now &lt;em&gt;this &lt;/em&gt;is the true reward that makes favors worthwhile, not the crummy wallpapers they give. 😆&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Bones told me he&amp;#8217;d love it if it would snow year-round! I strongly disagree with him about that.&lt;/p&gt;   &lt;div class="wp-block-image"&gt; &lt;figure class="aligncenter size-full"&gt;&lt;img width="400" height="299" src="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bones-snow-150x112.jpg" alt="Bones: It sure would be fun if it snowed all year long, for a bite!" class="wp-image-7837" sizes="auto, (max-width: 400px) 85vw, 400px" /&gt;&lt;figcaption class="wp-element-caption"&gt;For a bite? Yeah, &lt;em&gt;frostbite&lt;/em&gt; maybe.&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;p&gt;Have a great weekend, everyone! I&amp;#8217;ll be back again next week.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 	&lt;/div&gt;&lt;!-- .entry-content --&gt;  	&lt;footer class="entry-footer"&gt; 		&lt;span class="byline"&gt;&lt;img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/c27d879b16e3317f0d6fa350680e5023?s=98&amp;#038;d=mm&amp;#038;r=g' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49'/&gt;&lt;span class="screen-reader-text"&gt;Author &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="author vcard"&gt;&lt;a class="url fn n" href="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/author/jvgsjeff/"&gt;Jeff&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="posted-on"&gt;&lt;span class="screen-reader-text"&gt;Posted on &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.jvgs.net/acwwblog/2024/12/13/moon-from-the-stars/" rel="bookmark"&gt;&lt;time class="entry-date published" datetime="2024-12-13T22:23:32-05:00"&gt;December 13, 2024&lt;/time&gt;&lt;time class="updated" datetime="2024-12-13T22:27:20-05:00"&gt;December 13, 2024&lt;/time&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;			&lt;/footer&gt;&lt;!-- .entry-footer --&gt; &lt;/article&gt;</description>
